HEADWORD: Contractibility
<hw>Con*tract`i*bil"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>Capability of being contracted; quality of being contractible;
<as>as, the <ex>contractibility</ex> and dilatability of air</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Arbuthnot.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
